 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for NSW Ambulance said paramedics responded to the high-speed single vehicle crash where they assessed a teenage girl at the scene who sustained serious injuries.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales_Ambulance\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NSW Ambulance\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales_Ambulance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales_Ambulance\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was airlifted to Canberra Hospital.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\", \"score\": 0.9997600919723311, \"rank\": 0.00023996559725552994, \"text\": \"Canberra Hospital\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canberra_Hospital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daily  Today's top stories curated by our news team.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Grab a quick bite of today's latest news from around the region and the nation.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekdays  Catch up on the news of the day and unwind with great reading for your evening.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Get the editor's insights: what's happening & why it matters.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  Going out or staying in?\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Find out what's on.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Twice weekly  Stay in the know on news that matters to you with twice weekly newsletters from The Senior.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1678, \"en